{"tid":2025413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈有一樣野要做：價格戰","createTime":"2020-05-20T08:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T10:05:51.000Z","uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c4adccbf02e891d6f5743e4399e9b679f8b83aee","tid":2025413,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:29:43.000Z","msg":"唔撚標題黨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中資或藍紅店識得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以本傷人</span>時，我地係時候要用同一招數反擊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬥平</span></span><br />\n前題係<br />\n1. 夠錢畀所有基本嘅支出(包括營運資源，例如餐廳要用嘅食材)<br />\n2. 可以頂得住同級或更高嘅質素 (唔似pepe hk賣假貨)<br />\n3. 有足夠營利嚟持續營運<br />\n<br />\n滿足曬後，就要有咁平得咁平<br />\n<br />\n就係為左減少人血饅頭論<br />\n攻入藍絲貪平嘅死穴<br />\n記得請手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc990e0c3ee0a33674fdb36973a17451e3a136d6","tid":2025413,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"一定要賣淘寶貨"},{"pid":"d9fae1b4c9158ca1b8517e56e64b028ad96ceffe","tid":2025413,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc990e0c3ee0a33674fdb36973a17451e3a136d6","tid":2025413,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"一定要賣淘寶貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"唔一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊情況許可下"},{"pid":"0760c0bb34157f7310467059d3aacaa5c7e08d0d","tid":2025413,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"你都識講以本傷人啦"},{"pid":"f611d523adc68239350dd02e0f6377c3acf99367","tid":2025413,"uid":47239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"黃店小本經營點玩格價戰？<br />\n一陣又話要黃店捐錢又剩，咁邊有錢？"},{"pid":"ce3a691af1fd719a596e34d034ba9f3fb931eaf6","tid":2025413,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0760c0bb34157f7